Description: Open Data @ Tor Vergata is a project developed in collaboration with the Tor Vergata University Computing and Documentation Centre (CCD) and Etcware srl- on a 2007-2013 POR FESR (Regional Operational Programme- European Fund for Regional Development) grant funded by Filas for the Latium region.The goal of the project is to publish the administrative and teaching-related data of the University as open data. In addition- Etcware srl has developed Android and iOS applications for accessing teaching data primarily.
